"5   * Adjusted the Makefile to fix $(DESTDIR) problems.\n"
"6\n"
"7  -- Josip Rodin &lt;joy-mg@debian.org&gt;  Mon, 22 Mar 2010 00:37:31 +0100\n"
"8\n"
