msgid "If your package has manual pages, you should install them using <citerefentry> <refentrytitle>dh_installman</refentrytitle> <manvolnum>1</manvolnum> </citerefentry> by listing them in the <filename><replaceable>package</replaceable>.manpages</filename> files."
